          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>College Affordability and Innovation Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill provides incentives&nbsp;for institutions of higher education (IHEs) that receive federal financial aid to: (1) provide programs designed to decrease the cost and time required to obtain postsecondary degrees or certificates; and (2) meet accountability standards that focus on affordability, accessibility for low- and middle-income students, and value.</p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2018-09-27</actionDate>
        </item>
